p.d: The Boat Show takes you on board the most beautiful boats in the world, from inflatable boats to superyachts, both sailing and motor boats. Maximum speed, fuel consumption, habitability, technical details, but also tips for choosing the boat of your dreams. Jump on board the boat of your dreams with The Boat Show!
